<sect1 id="dir_d368ce8d6920c000d21f916ca5b7e02f_1autotoc_md160">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::combat</title><para>Combat-related gameplay systems, components, and commands.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_d368ce8d6920c000d21f916ca5b7e02f_1autotoc_md161">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides all building blocks for implementing combat mechanics such as aiming, shooting, projectile spawning, and attack attribution.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_d368ce8d6920c000d21f916ca5b7e02f_1autotoc_md162">
<title>Submodules</title><para><table rows="5" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Submodule  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>commands/</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Commands for combat actions (ShootCommand, Aim2DCommand)  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>components/</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Data containers for combat state (aiming, cooldowns, attack tracking)  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
